name: 币安汽车 (Bianqiche)
description: According to BlockBeats, on October 8th, GMGN market data showed that the market capitalization of the BSC ecosystem meme coin "Binance Auto" exceeded $30 million, currently trading at $34 million, with trading volume reaching $33 million within the first hour of its launch. Faraday Future founder Jia Yueting reportedly posted an image of a car with the "BNB" logo on the X platform, captioned: "Drive a Binance Auto, enjoy the Binance life."
